data.description: Move-in Ready Beautiful Craftsman Style End Unit Townhome that backs to greenspace! Covered porch welcomes you to this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home with privacy at end of street. Beautiful kitchen with cherry cabinets, granite counters & modern appliances all new in 2023 and ALL included, as well as washer and dryer & flat screen TV. Lovely open floorplan with high ceilings, lots of natural light. Upstairs a retreat awaits in huge primary suite with coved ceiling, walk in closet and double sink vanity. Laundry room also upstairs with full size washer/dryer & two more bedrooms plus full bath. Fenced backyard with patio and grass also has dedicated dog run for your furry companion. Well maintained with exterior painted in 2023. Great home in a very desirable area with low HOA! Easy access to Clackamas Community College, shopping, golf, walking trails. This is an incredible value, don't wait to check this home out - OPEN HOUSE Saturday 1/27, Noon-2pm!
